<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>As a long-time reader and only occasional poster,i see the vast majority of posts on this and other threads fall into 2 categories:Gear or Plat.I'd like to know more about in-game strategies,battle techniques,etc.Its been my experience that an averagely equipped paladin who has mastered the complexities of this hybrid-tank class is more valuable to his/her group than someone more concerned with out-dps'ing party members with thier uber-gear could hope to be.Now,to the question........I play a paladin in a small family guild and usually serve as MT,and since we dont raid much I rarely get to see other pally's in action or query them as to the finer points of performing that role into the high-end game(60+ zones).I wont ask for the Paladin Bible right here but any knowledgable fellow paladins who can direct me to a source of actual usefull info (hopefully devoid of insignificant chest-pounding) would help me tremendously.Alternately,if you have tips and tricks of the trade you'd like to share with me that would also help.                 Many thanks =)</p>
